  "description": "## Deep Component Audit — hx-avatar\n\n**Component directory:** `packages/hx-library/src/components/hx-avatar/`\n**wc-mcp Health Score:** 100 (A) — No issues.\n\n### Audit Scope\n1. **Design Tokens** — `--hx-` tokens only. No hardcoded values. Three-tier cascade. Dark mode.\n2. **Accessibility** — WCAG 2.1 AA. Alt text for images. Fallback initials. ARIA labels.\n3. **Functionality** — Image loading/error fallback. Initials generation. Size variants. Shape variants. Status indicator.\n4. **TypeScript** — Strict. No `any`.\n5. **CSS/Styling** — Shadow DOM. CSS Parts. Responsive sizing.\n6. **CEM Accuracy** — Verify 100 score holds.\n7. **Tests** — 80%+ coverage. Image error fallback. Initials. Sizes.\n8. **Storybook** — All sizes/shapes/states. Image + fallback demos.\n9. **Drupal Compatibility** — Twig-friendly. User profile integration.\n10. **Portability** — CDN-ready.\n\n### Deliverable\nDetailed audit report. Fix CRITICAL+HIGH. Document rest.",
